    Create table for human delay parameters

    delay_table.Rd

    Create table for human delay parameters

    Usage

    delay_table(df, pathogen)

    Arguments

    df

    processed data with parameter information produced using data_param_table()

    pathogen

    name of pathogen

    Value

    flextable with an overview of the delay parameter estimates extracted from the included studies

    Examples

    df <- data_param_table(pathogen = "marburg", exclude = c(15, 17))
